item.title: CVE-2023-43089|2024-08-02T19:37:23.193Z -- dell -- dell%20rugged%20control%20center
item.description: Dell Rugged Control Center, version prior to 4.7, contains insufficient protection for the Policy folder. A local malicious standard user could potentially exploit this vulnerability to modify the content of the policy file, leading to unauthorized access to resources.
